<br>
Gnome clothing: <br>
Ac=20, int=9, agi=3, dex=4, cha=2, sta=3, mana=43<br>
<br>
Gnome spellbook item:<br>
int=5, cha=5, hp=10, mana=20<br>
<br>
High Elf Clothing:<br>
Ac=20, int=12, agi=6, dex=7, cha=6, sta=0, mana=10<br>
<br>
Seems like those early quests (and items) could make a big difference (or at least be a salient consideration for Gnome versus High Elf mages.<br>
<br>
<br>
